# Public site theme — cinematic

The marketing site uses **`data-theme="public"`** via `PublicSiteLayout`. The coaching dashboard uses **`data-theme="app"`** (orange shadcn primary) — do not change dashboard styling when editing public pages.

## Tokens and CSS

- Design tokens and utilities live in [client/src/styles/cinematic.css](client/src/styles/cinematic.css) (`--nb-bg`, `--nb-ink`, `--nb-accent`, etc.).
- Page shell: `className="nb-page"` on the page root (layout also sets `nb-page`).
- Primary CTA: **`nb-btn-primary`** (green gradient). Do **not** use shadcn `<Button variant="default">` alone on public CTAs (inherits orange from app theme).
- Secondary CTA: **`nb-btn-secondary`** or `CinematicSecondaryCTA`.
- Typography: `nb-display`, `nb-body`, `nb-mono-label`, `SectionLabel` from `@/components/public-cinematic/`.

## Header and footer

- `SiteHeader`: fixed, scroll-aware blur; logo uses `nb-logo-invert`; nav links unchanged (`/`, `/about`, `/speaking`, `/resources`, `/pricing`, `/login`, `/intake`).
- `SiteFooter`: dark cinematic three-column layout; newsletter + legal links.

## Forms on public routes

- Intake and similar forms: wrap inputs in **`public-form-light`** so fields stay light/readable on the dark page shell.

## Removed (do not reintroduce)

- `tesoro-cta-gradient`, `hero-accent-phrase`, `problems-accent-shimmer`
- Light marketing strips (`bg-neutral-50` as default page background)
- `data-theme="site"` (renamed to `public`)

## After changes

- Load homepage: dark cinematic hero, lime accent, green CTA — not orange, not white full-page background.
- Load `/consultant` or `/client`: dashboard still orange/ember.
